         <abstract id="aspace_87ab01dfcf9dc28434923c66f2a1a60e">The collection consists of autograph manuscripts, documents and correspondence of people in public life. The collection contains correspondence of Theodore Roosevelt with Francis J. Heney and others and copies of letters of the Jonathan Knight family.</abstract>
